                <p>
                Let <m>h(x) = -x^{4} + 4 \, x^{3} + 3 \, x + 3</m>. Explain and demonstrate how to find an equation for the line tangent to the graph of <m>h(x)</m> at the point <m>(3, 39)</m>.
